section.section:
Each county public library system that participates in the minimum library program shall be provided for each resident of the county, to be used for operating and capital expenses:
For each of fiscal years 2011 through 2016 - $14.00;
For fiscal year 2017 - $14.30;
For fiscal year 2018 - $14.60; and
For fiscal year 2019 and each fiscal year thereafter - $15.00.
